      <title>如果無法履行債務義務，Fisker可能在30天內尋求破產保護</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/fisker-may-seek-bankruptcy-protection-30-days-if-unable-meet-debt-obligations-2024-04-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲斯克在周二向監管機構提交的文件中披露，如果未能從債權人處獲得足夠的救濟，也無法獲得足夠的流動性來履行當前的債務義務，菲斯克可能必須在 30 天內申請破產保護。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/fisker-may-seek-bankruptcy-protection-30-days-if-unable-meet-debt-obligations-2024-04-23/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 12:32:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
